OL,3,CCampaigner 'over the moon' as
OL,4,CHillsborough Law returns to Commons
OL,6,FA campaigner whose son died in the
OL,7,FHillsborough disaster says she is
OL,8,F"over the moon" amid news a proposed
OL,9,Flaw to improve accountability in
OL,10,Fpublic office is likely to clear the
OL,11,FHouse of Commons.
OL,13,FThe law change, officially known as
OL,14,Fthe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,15,FBill, would create a legally-
OL,16,Fenforceable duty of candour which
OL,17,Fcompels public officials and
OL,18,Fauthorities to act transparently when
OL,19,Finvestigations and inquiries take
OL,20,Fplace.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
