CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783961289
OL,3,CCampaigner 'over the moon' as
OL,4,CHillsborough Law returns to Commons
OL,6,FIt takes its name from the
OL,7,FHillsborough disaster in 1989 when 97
OL,8,FLiverpool fans were killed at the
OL,9,Ffootball stadium in Sheffield in a
OL,10,Fcrush during an FA Cup semi-final
OL,11,Fmatch.
OL,13,FMargaret Aspinall, whose 18-year-old
OL,14,Fson James died in the disaster, told
OL,15,Fthe Daily Mirror she was "absolutely
OL,16,Fdelighted, over the moon, absolutely
OL,17,Fmade up".
OL,26,@wD@ZOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783961289
OL,3,CCampaigner 'over the moon' as
OL,4,CHillsborough Law returns to Commons
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy said
OL,7,Fhe was "confident" the draft
OL,8,Flegislation would be back "in the
OL,9,Fcoming days" at the despatch box last
OL,10,Fweek, but other Government figures
OL,11,Fsuggested it would not return until
OL,12,Fafter the summer recess.
OL,14,FIf passed, the Bill could form one of
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer's last acts as Prime
OL,16,FMinister.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@RO]pD@[OUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
