PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783961289
OL,3,CCampaigner 'over the moon' as
OL,4,CHillsborough Law returns to Commons
OL,6,FMs Aspinall, who chairs the
OL,7,FHillsborough Family Support group,
OL,8,Ftold the newspaper: "When I was
OL,9,Fspeaking to Keir Starmer, I told him
OL,10,Fthis would be a lovely legacy for you
OL,11,Fto leave behind.
OL,13,F"I always believed he wanted to give
OL,14,Fus the Hillsborough Law. It was others
OL,15,Fstopping him. Now it's done."
OL,17,FShe continued: "Our families have
OL,18,Fworked hard for this, but it's not for
OL,19,Fus, it's for the country. We've done
OL,20,Fit for the people of this country. I'm
OL,21,Fso proud.
OL,26,@pD@UOUuD@AOUwD@]O]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
